nt-weight: 400;\"> across its global agricultural ecosystem.<\/span><\/p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">As a platform that integrates commercial agricultural trade, digital infrastructure, and mission-driven impact<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">, IFU is structured to maintain clear oversight, ethical operations, and compliance with international standards.<\/span><\/p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">\u00a0<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1fefde76 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"1fefde76\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-5fa01530 elementor-widget elementor-widget-cherito-about\" data-id=\"5fa01530\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"cherito-about.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<section class=\"about-one section-space\">\r\n\t\t<div class=\"about-one__bg\"><\/div><!-- \/.about-one__bg -->\r\n\t\t<div class=\"container\">\r\n\t\t\t<div class=\"row gutter-y-50\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-lg-6\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"about-one__content\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"sec-title wow fadeInUp\" data-wow-duration=\"1500ms\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"sec-title__title\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tGovernance Structure\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/h3><!-- \/.sec-title__title -->\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div><!-- \/.sec-title -->\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"about-one__text-box wow fadeInUp\" data-wow-duration=\"1500ms\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"about-one__text\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tIFU\u2019s governance model is designed to support both its commercial platform operations and its social impact mission, through a clearly defined and balanced structure:\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/p>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<