\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tIFU Foundation Governance\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/h3><!-- \/.sec-title__title -->\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div><!-- \/.sec-title -->\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"about-six__text-box wow fadeInUp\" data-wow-duration=\"1500ms\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"about-six__text\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tThe IFU Foundation operates under its own governance structure to ensure that all charitable activities\u2014including farmer training, rural development, and school meal programs\u2014are managed with integrity, transparency, and compliance with nonprofit standards.\n<BR><BR>\n<strong>Core Governance Principles<\/strong><BR>\nIFU\u2019s governance framework is guided by the following principles:\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/p>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div><!-- \/.about-six__text-box -->\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<ul class=\"about-six__list list-unstyled wow fadeInUp\" data-wow-duration=\"1500ms\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"about-six__list__icon\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<i aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"icon-check\"><\/i>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tTransparency:\nOpen communication, clear reporting, and accessible information across all levels of the organization.\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/li>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"about-six__list__icon\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<i aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"icon-check\"><\/i>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tAccountability:\nDefined roles and responsibilities, with measurable performance and oversight mechanisms.\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/li>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"about-six__lis